00:50:53,810 --> 00:50:57,480
You really could've died, Jae Won.

534
00:50:58,810 --> 00:51:01,680
Whose side is Nam Tae Ju on?

535
00:51:01,680 --> 00:51:04,190
Kwon Yeong Ik? Kwon Yun Jin?

536
00:51:04,190 --> 00:51:05,900
Is this really what Sun Yeong would want?

537
00:51:05,900 --> 00:51:08,590
