 - Will you really be okay like this?

538
00:51:08,590 --> 00:51:10,210
To find out what they're thinking—

539
00:51:10,210 --> 00:51:13,180
How long do you think you can ignore me?

540
00:51:15,390 --> 00:51:19,180
I won't disappear, Jae Won.

541
00:51:45,260 --> 00:51:47,590
 You can't go in there!

