00:52:21,880 --> 00:52:23,370
 Seung Gyu...

553
00:52:23,370 --> 00:52:26,150
 Seung Gyu fell from the rooftop.

554
00:52:26,150 --> 00:52:29,880
 It couldn't be helped because he threatened to kill us both.

555
00:52:31,090 --> 00:52:32,860
 Is he dead?

556
00:52:35,220 --> 00:52:37,880
 What do I do now, Father?

557
00:52:40,890 --> 00:52:43,100
 Come home immediately.

558
00:52:43,950 --> 00:52:50,270
Is this the audio file you've been so desperately looking for?

559
00:52:50,270 --> 00:52:54,990
