562
00:53:00,580 --> 00:53:02,510
But if this file gets released,

563
00:53:02,510 --> 00:53:07,230
it won't matter if Baek Seung Gyu was pushed or not.

564
00:53:08,130 --> 00:53:13,010
What matters is you knew about this but tried to cover it up.

565
00:53:14,190 --> 00:53:16,420
On top of that...

566
00:53:16,420 --> 00:53:18,010
Seung Gyu's awake.

567
00:53:18,010 --> 00:53:20,600
Do you think...

568
00:53:20,600 --> 00:53:22,430
I'll just let you be?

569
00:53:22,430 --> 00:53:24,530
Don't let me be.

570
00:53:25,670 --> 00:53:29,030
- What did you say?
 - You'll have to decide before you come.

571
00:53:30,560 --> 00:53:33,610
Whether to protect your minister position

572
00:53:34,910 --> 00:53:37,550
or your daughter.

